{"type":"message","id":"bb902482","parentId":"7f2fb7de","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:08:14.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看起来你当前用的是 GLM-Plus (zhipu/glm-4-plus)，fallback 是 Kimi。\n\n切换模型报错可能是几个原因：\n1. 模型别名拼写不对\n2. 那个模型没配置 API key\n3. 或者用的是 `/model` 而不是 `/switch`\n\n你当时是怎么操作的？把报错信息给我看看，我帮你排查一下。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":343,"output":82,"cacheRead":15616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16041,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773850092177}}
