{"type":"message","id":"eb56da54","parentId":"ca96146d","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:08:53.347Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哈哈，找到问题了！🎯\n\n你输入的是 `moonshot/glm-4-plus`，但 GLM-4-Plus 是智谱的模型，不是 Moonshot 的。\n\n正确的写法应该是：\n- `/switch zhipu/glm-4-plus` （完整路径）\n- 或者直接 `/switch GLM-Plus` （用别名更简单）\n\nMoonshot 家的模型是 Kimi 系列，比如 `moonshot/kimi-k2.5`。\n\n要我帮你切到 GLM-Plus 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":247,"output":111,"cacheRead":15872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16230,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773850129694}}
