{"type":"message","id":"1246ee07","parentId":"6b9a814a","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:09:44.231Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"配置文件看起来是对的，GLM-4-Plus 在 `zhipu` provider 下定义得好好的。\n\n问题是你输入了 `moonshot/glm-4-plus`，但 GLM-4-Plus 属于 `zhipu` provider，不是 `moonshot`。所以系统报 \"model not allowed\" 是因为它在 moonshot 下找不到这个模型。\n\n正确的切换方式：\n- `/switch zhipu/glm-4-plus`\n- 或者直接用别名 `/switch GLM-Plus`\n\n不是配置文件错了，是 provider 前缀搞混了 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":6446,"output":121,"cacheRead":16640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23207,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773850179449}}
{"type":"message","id":"2dee4e88","parentId":"1246ee07","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:10:48.973Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-19 00:10 GMT+8] 那你能修改吗"}],"timestamp":1773850248971}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee38e7fc","parentId":"2dee4e88","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:10:54.277Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"修改什么？是指：\n\n1. **修改默认模型** - 把默认从 Kimi 换成 GLM-Plus？\n2. **添加别名** - 让 `/switch glm-4-plus` 这种写法也能用？\n3. **还是别的需求**？\n\n告诉我你想怎么改，我帮你弄。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":16006,"output":68,"cacheRead":7168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23242,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773850248972}}
